00:12:00.040 --> 00:12:05.600
OK. In retrospect, I should have
listened to our friends who scoffed

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:08.000
when we solicited recommendations
for a cat sitter.

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:10.720
"The cat will be fine," they said.

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:13.900
"You're going away for a
long weekend, not a month.

00:12:13.900 --> 00:12:18.030
Just leave some food and water and
the cat will take care of himself."

00:12:18.030 --> 00:12:21.880
But George Harrison, the cat,
not the Beatle, was our baby

00:12:21.880 --> 00:12:25.040
and he had this bad habit of
wedging himself into spaces

00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:26.790
from which he could not escape

00:12:26.790 --> 00:12:28.750
like between the refrigerator
and the wall.

00:12:28.750 --> 00:12:32.300 position:56%
And I had horrible visions of him
slowly starving to death while James

00:12:32.300 --> 00:12:33.710 position:56%
and I drank wine with an ocean view.

00:12:33.710 --> 00:12:36.880
So we found a cat sitter online.

00:12:36.880 --> 00:12:40.350
Her name is Megan and she had
hair the color of cotton candy.

00:12:40.350 --> 00:12:42.760
I didn't like the way
that she looked at James,

00:12:42.760 --> 00:12:44.670 position:56%
the way her mascaraed lashes drooped

00:12:44.670 --> 00:12:47.510
and her teeth caught
her glossy lips,

00:12:47.510 --> 00:12:50.820
but James said it was
all in my head.

00:12:50.820 --> 00:12:53.090
Besides, George Harrison
seemed to like her curling

00:12:53.090 --> 00:12:55.430
around her tattooed
ankles almost immediately

00:12:55.430 --> 00:12:57.410
and that was all that mattered.

00:12:57.410 --> 00:13:01.410
Our trip went a bit sideways
when someone stole my purse,

00:13:01.410 --> 00:13:03.160
which had my driver's
license inside,

00:13:03.160 --> 00:13:06.490
which meant I no longer had
the identification necessary

00:13:06.490 --> 00:13:08.170
to board an airplane.

00:13:08.170 --> 00:13:11.410
It could have been a complete
disaster, but Megan happily went

00:13:11.410 --> 00:13:13.810
to our place, followed
our directions

00:13:13.810 --> 00:13:17.600
to unlock a specific desk
drawer, and found my passport,

00:13:17.600 --> 00:13:20.010
