00:29:07.360 --> 00:29:09.220
Meanwhile, the fire had
spread to the walls.

00:29:09.220 --> 00:29:11.010
The front of the store collapsed.

00:29:11.010 --> 00:29:13.110
Smoke whirled toward
Jake like a sheet.

00:29:13.110 --> 00:29:14.960
He dragged himself away from it.

00:29:14.960 --> 00:29:17.000
"The entrance should be
this way, shouldn't it?"

00:29:17.000 --> 00:29:18.370
