00:29:18.370 --> 00:29:21.940 position:56%
He was blind in the dark,
coughing, his foot bursting in pain.

00:29:21.940 --> 00:29:24.360
Smoke filled his mouth until
it felt like something solid

00:29:24.360 --> 00:29:26.140
