00:51:54.910 --> 00:51:59.220
Ivy always gave me that look.

00:51:59.220 --> 00:52:02.840
Her tight, prissy little lip twist.

00:52:02.840 --> 00:52:05.410
The laugh I could see
right behind her eyes.

00:52:05.410 --> 00:52:07.310
