coffee in between.

00:57:25.510 --> 00:57:26.810
The letter I found written

00:57:26.810 --> 00:57:28.810
in that prissy tight
handwriting lay open on the table.

00:57:28.810 --> 00:57:30.750
I read it maybe 100 times.

00:57:30.750 --> 00:57:33.120
Ivy still made those little
curlicue shapes on her y's

00:57:33.120 --> 00:57:35.000
like she hadn't grown up at all.

00:57:35.000 --> 00:57:37.560
I bid on both pies after the
contest, had to pay a lot more

00:57:37.560 --> 00:57:40.250
for Jean's than mine, of course.

00:57:40.250 --> 00:57:42.130
The headlights skidded across
the windows and I looked up,

00:57:42.130 --> 00:57:44.010
my heart beat slowing to a thud.

00:57:44.010 --> 00:57:47.070
I folded Ivy's note and
put it in my apron pocket.

00:57:47.070 --> 00:57:50.750
My legs tingled when I stood up
and went to shut off the radio.

00:57:50.750 --> 00:57:52.990
The clock told me I'd been
sitting there for over an hour.

00:57:52.990 --> 00:57:55.610
I'd eaten almost half of both pies.

00:57:55.610 --> 00:57:57.100
The kitchen door rattled open.

00:57:57.100 --> 00:57:59.900
