said, her cheeks flushed.

00:57:59.900 --> 00:58:03.070
She pulled her hat off and let her
hair spill down over her shoulders.

00:58:03.070 --> 00:58:04.610
"Gone?" I asked.

00:58:04.610 --> 00:58:06.280
"They're dead," Jean said.

00:58:06.280 --> 00:58:07.980
"Break failure out on
the new two-lane highway.

00:58:07.980 --> 00:58:09.800
Headlong collision
with a big wheeler.

00:58:09.800 --> 00:58:11.940
Marvin's tow truck was parked at
the edge of the Fall Fest lot.

00:58:11.940 --> 00:58:13.870
Just took one snip."

00:58:13.870 --> 00:58:15.170
