00:58:20.170 --> 00:58:21.470
"He'll live.

00:58:21.470 --> 00:58:22.770
It's all perfect."

00:58:22.770 --> 00:58:24.540
Jean put her hands on my
cheeks and pulled me close.

00:58:24.540 --> 00:58:28.030 position:56%
